  "display_fullname": "Dominator Assault Radioactive Assault Atom Smasher",
  "display_help": "You charge up a dangerously unstable amount of radioactive energy into a single fist before driving it into the ground and causing a small explosion. Foes caught in the blast will suffer High Energy and Toxic damage and have their defense reduced. Enemies also have a moderate chance to be disoriented for a short time. Affected enemies have a small chance to be affected by the Contaminated effect. Hitting Contaminated foes with single target Radioactive Assault powers cause a small burst of damage to foes near the target.<br><br><color #fcfc95>Damage: Moderate.</color><br><color #fcfc95>Recharge: Slow.</color>",
